{
  "id": "4-1",
  "title": "Act 1: The Expedition",
  "startNode": "main",
  "nodes": {
    "main": {
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "marker",
          "id": "ch4_act1_start"
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "blackout",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "scanlines",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "titleCard",
          "args": {
            "text": "Chapter 4: At the Shield's Edge"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 2500
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The outer wall of the power node was covered in rust.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Deep crimson rust that looked like congealed blood under the sickly light of the perimeter lamps, spreading down the massive cylindrical structure from its crown to its base.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The shield's edge lay just ahead. That translucent luminous barrier glowed faintly blue-white against the dark sky, a thin membrane separating this world from the one beyond.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "From here, one could clearly see that the shield's density had become uneven. Several sections were noticeably darker than others, and through those dark areas, the outline of the wasteland was barely visible.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Soren",
          "text": "Supply station. Used by Terminal Ark's frontier operations. Constructed approximately twenty years ago. This location marks the outermost boundary of Ark territory.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "He shifted his gaze toward the heavy vehicles parked against the building's side.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Soren",
          "text": "Active power signatures. Someone is inside.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Elias",
          "text": "More than that. Strong mechanical neural signals, highly concentrated and perfectly arranged—<em>artificial soldiers</em>, and quite a few of them. Looks like a regular power recharge cycle.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Alea",
          "text": "Soldiers in recharge are offline. If we can get what we need and leave before they complete their cycle, there won't be any conflict.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Soren",
          "text": "In theory.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "They chose a side ventilation grate as their entry point. Elias unlocked its electronic mechanism, and the four of them slipped inside, crawling through the building's internal ductwork.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "vignette",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The interior of the supply station was far more spacious than expected. The central hall was a two-story high storage chamber.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The walls were covered with dense charging racks, each holding a recharging artificial soldier.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Heads slightly bowed, optical sensors dark, chest and shoulders connected to thick power conduits. Pale blue light flowed slowly through the conduits.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Twelve of them. Alea counted silently.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Along the hall's perimeter, storage shelves held what they needed—neural stabilizers, medical supply packs, and several combat augmentation modules hung on the wall, their casings still gleaming with factory finish.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Soren",
          "text": "<whisper>Quick. Take only what we need, don't touch anything else.</whisper>",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "They split up, moving carefully. Lyra went for the medical supplies, Elias for the stabilizers, Soren to evaluate the augmentation module types.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Alea remained in the center of the hall, maintaining watch. Her gaze swept back and forth across the twelve silent forms.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The blue light in the power conduits suddenly stopped flowing.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Alea's body reacted before her conscious mind caught up. She stepped backward, her spine pressing against the nearest load-bearing column.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Alea",
          "text": "<whisper>Stop. Don't move.</whisper>",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "A moment of silence filled the hall.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "shake",
          "ms": 500,
          "args": {
            "intensity": 6
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Then every artificial soldier's optical sensors <em>ignited simultaneously</em>.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Cold white light, perfectly synchronized, utterly devoid of emotion. When twelve points of light flared in darkness at the same instant, it felt as though the entire hall's atmosphere had been violently crushed.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "shake",
          "ms": 400,
          "args": {
            "intensity": 8
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The locking mechanisms on the charging racks disengaged in sequence, conduits disconnected. The soldier frames stepped down from their mounts with no preparatory motion whatsoever.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Metal feet hitting the floor with heavy, synchronized, perfectly metronomic precision.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "text": ">> Intruder identified — Combat directives taking priority override",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Lyra",
          "text": "Alea—",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Alea",
          "text": "Listen to me. Three of you equip those augmentation modules and follow my lead.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The first artificial soldier began advancing toward her.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1500
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "ms": 800,
          "args": {
            "stay": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "vignette",
          "args": {
            "enabled": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "scanlines",
          "args": {
            "enabled": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "end"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "onComplete": [
    "complete"
  ]
}
